h Moo-hyun 3.jpg|{{flagicon|Korea, South|1997}} [[Roh Moo-hyun]] File:Muammar al-Gaddafi-09122003.jpg|{{flagicon|Libya|1977}} '''[[Muammar Gaddafi]]''' File:Badawi AID.jpg|{{flagicon|Malaysia}} [[Abdullah Ahmad Badawi]] File:Felipe Calderon 20090130.jpg|{{flagicon|Mexico}} [[Felipe Calderón]] File:Vicente Fox flag.jpg|{{flagicon|Mexico}} [[Vicente Fox]] File:Jan Peter Balkenende 2006.jpg|{{flagicon| Netherlands}} [[Jan Peter Balkenende]] File:Helen Clark UNDP 2010.jpg|{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Helen Clark]] File:Annemarie Huber-Hotz.jpg|{{flagicon|Switzerland}} [[Annemarie Huber-Hotz]] File:Corina Casanova 2011.jpg|{{flagicon|Switzerland}} [[Corina Casanova]] File:Mahmoud Abbas 2007.jpg|{{flagicon|Palestinian National Authority}} [[Mahmoud Abbas]] File:YasserArafat.jpg|{{flagicon|Palestinian National Authority}} [[Yasser Arafat]] File:Pervez Musharraf 2004.jpg|{{flagicon|Pakistan}} [[Pervez Musharraf]] File:Gloria Macapagal Arroyo WEF 2009-crop.jpg|{{flagicon|Philippines}} [[Gloria Macapagal Arroyo]] File:Aleksander kwasniewski konferencja.jpg|{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Aleksander Kwaśniewski]] File:Lech Kaczyński.jpg|{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Lech Kaczyński]] File:Ion Iliescu (2004) (cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Romania}} [[Ion Iliescu]] File:Flickr - europeanpeoplesparty - EPP Congress Rome 2006 (76).jpg|{{flagicon|Romania}} [[Traian Băsescu]] File:Abdullah of Saudi Arabia.jpg|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[Abdullah of Saudi Arabia|Abdullah bin Abdulaziz Al Saud]] File:Fahd bin Abdul Aziz.jpg|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[Fahd of Saudi Arabia|Fahd bin Abdulaziz Al Saud]] File:Aznar at the Azores, March 17, 2003-2.jpg|{{flagicon|Spain}} [[José María Aznar]] File:Lee Hsien Loong 2004-11-21.jpg|{{flagicon|Singapore}} [[Lee Hsien Loong]] File:SthAfrica.ThaboMbeki.01.jpg|{{flagicon|South Africa}} [[Thabo Mbeki]] File:José Luis Rodríguez Zapatero 2009 (cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Spain}} [[José Luis Rodríguez Zapatero]] File:Goran Persson, Sveriges statsminister, talar vid Nordiska radets se